Description: Optional applications installer for GNOME
 Obision Install is a modern GTK4/Libadwaita application that provides
 a simple interface to install and manage applications on your system.
 .
 Features:
  - Support for Flatpak and APT packages
  - GNOME app folders integration
  - Application categories organization
  - Modern GNOME interface
